summary.name: Central Hostel Milano
summary.tagline: Guesthouse connected to the convention center, within easy reach of Corso Buenos Aires

editorial.title: Milan
content: Located in Central Station neighborhood, Central Hostel Milano is connected to a rail/subway station. Cathedral of Milan and Teatro alla Scala are notable landmarks, and travelers looking to shop may want to visit Galleria Vittorio Emanuele II. Looking to enjoy an event or a game while in town? See what's happening at San Siro Stadium or Autodromo Nazionale Monza. Spend some time exploring the area's activities, including outlet shopping.
